Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:19.99,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,虽然没有明显外伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:24.38,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,但是父亲的头部受到撞击  失去意识
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.85,0:00:28.88,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,贤治从昏迷中醒来后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:32.52,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,他变得跟过去判若两人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.46,0:00:38.39,Default,Sakura,0,0,0,,他的主体性和定向力大幅降低
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.79,0:00:42.52,Default,Sakura,0,0,0,,推测头部因强烈的冲击而产生了障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.09,0:00:45.17,Default,Sakura,0,0,0,,因此  我告诉家属
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:49.15,Default,Sakura,0,0,0,,让超级 AI MICHI 进行治疗才是最有希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.60,0:00:55.20,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,但是… 把人力所不能及的问题交给超级 AI 处理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:58.13,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,这是我父亲最讨厌的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:07.29,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,而后藤的家属们找到的希望之光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:13.64,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,那就是贤治的孙女  莉音的「歌声」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.17,0:01:20.11,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,爷爷  你听到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:22.06,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:26.82,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,继续努力  继续努力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.04,0:01:30.33,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,在接触到音乐和电影时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:36.03,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,贤治受损的回路中  恢复了人性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.62,0:01:40.16,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,这是人类之手所创造的  艺术的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:44.62,Default,Announcer,0,0,0,,后藤一家的努力才刚刚开始
Comment: 0,0:01:47.22,0:01:50.58,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,我们(日本仿生人权利组织,Humanoid Rights Japan)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.22,0:01:50.58,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,我们日本仿生人权利组织
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:53.17,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,不认为这是什么值得宣传的美谈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:56.93,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,明明有治好他电子脑的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.93,0:01:58.18,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,但家属却拒绝治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:02:00.35,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,这是对老人的忽视
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:04.62,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,意识是非常敏感的领域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:08.44,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,不接受超级 AI 精神治疗的例子也不罕见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:11.69,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,那用人类的力量治疗就行了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.69,0:02:13.67,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,可以吗  须堂医生？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:17.95,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,先让他来一趟诊所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:20.11,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,十分感谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:58.00,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,这种治疗责任重大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:04:01.51,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,所以普通的医生都是交给超级 AI 来做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:05.03,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,但是须堂医生的医术是值得信赖的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:12.14,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,看起来硬件损伤并没有很严重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:18.15,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,负责个性基础的部位应该都没有受损
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:22.90,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,如果能安装一些系统来弥补损失的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:26.45,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,令尊的病症应该能被治好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:28.66,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:32.13,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:34.08,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,现有的媒体都不能信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:38.44,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,我们必须要成为第一手信源才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:41.52,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,我之后再打给你  先挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:43.29,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,情况怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:46.38,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,医生说能治好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.38,0:04:48.39,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,那么  手术安排到哪一天了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:52.10,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,不… 我们还没决定要进行手术…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:54.32,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:57.67,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,是要安装和以前不同的程序吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:05:00.83,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,人装上义肢之后  不也还是同一个人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:04.06,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,但是义肢和电子脑不是一回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:05.18,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:08.74,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,但是在脑袋里  也有部位是能被替换的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:11.04,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,所以应该也没什么区别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:17.08,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,你到底在犹豫什么  真让人搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:20.78,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,明明眼前就有切实可行的治疗方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:24.00,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我无法保证一定能恢复如初哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:30.29,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,毕竟的确有数据因物理损伤无法找回了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:35.31,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:37.73,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,好了  回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.16,0:05:47.85,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,让我再考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:58.24,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,夕阳中的红蜻蜓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:07.17,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,上次看到你停在人背上已是何时？
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.17,0:06:10.99,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,山中田地里的…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.99,0:06:12.19,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,你怎么看？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:13.56,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,你是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:15.08,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,须堂医生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:21.33,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,我感觉他们家不愿意治好贤治  是有苦衷的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:22.40,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,苦衷？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:26.83,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,他女儿好像想成为歌手或者艺人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:28.40,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,所以  你觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:33.53,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,你是说  他们家是利用现况来换取关注？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:37.46,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,不管有什么苦衷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:40.92,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,拒绝接受有效的治疗是侵犯人权
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:49.43,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,他们会接受手术吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:51.84,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:55.91,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,这不是我能决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:02.64,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,这么晚了  是谁打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:12.41,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,非常抱歉  这么晚打来电话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:16.66,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,但是我想今天内和您谈谈
Comment: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:20.02,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,我们(日本仿生人权利组织,Humanoid Rights Japan)认为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.66,0:07:20.02,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,我们日本仿生人权利组织认为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:23.43,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,拒绝治疗后藤贤治是很严重的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:31.85,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,「所有人类生而自由  在尊严和权利上一律平等」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:38.08,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,1948 年签署的 世界人权宣言的第一条如是记载
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:42.79,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,这里的「人类」不包含仿生人
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.79,0:07:45.56,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,仿生人在历史的舞台上登场
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.56,0:07:47.33,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,与人类共同生存
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.33,0:07:49.83,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,到取得现有的人权
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.83,0:07:51.72,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,他们历经了艰难曲折
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:56.47,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,最终  随着超级 AI 的出现
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:59.33,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}时代发生了巨大的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:14.38,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,杰  追加模组的安装已完成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:17.39,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,以我来看也没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:21.18,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,现在进行生物躯体缝合术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:22.39,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:24.90,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,你感觉还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.86,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,没事的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:30.15,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,好  那就把一切给恢复如初
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:33.46,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,生命体征全部正常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:46.46,Default,Rion,0,0,0,,爷爷没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:49.97,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,一定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.97,0:08:52.81,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,我们全家人一起迎接他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:02.68,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,你也真够缠人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.31,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,又来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:05.73,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:11.39,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,记录后藤的恢复过程也是我们的活动内容嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:13.86,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,要把照明器材搬到二楼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.82,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,嗯  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.17,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,借过一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.17,0:09:18.10,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:20.27,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,喂喂  这里可是医院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:23.89,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,我可是有取得病人家属的许可才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:26.08,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,他们不是挺好的一家人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:28.17,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,才不像是你所说的那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:29.38,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,医生！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:32.13,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,病人发狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:35.75,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,父亲！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:38.39,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,你这个忘恩负义的蠢儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:41.39,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,我可是全都知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.96,0:09:43.89,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,贤  贤治？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:48.00,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,给我拍视频让我出丑  你竟敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:49.67,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,后藤先生 请息怒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:50.40,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.07,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,你误会了  父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:55.53,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,我只是想遵守你的教导
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:59.43,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,觉得这能成为其他患者的希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:02.16,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,你搞什么名堂！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:04.35,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,父亲  请息怒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:06.04,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,丽莎  镇定剂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:07.62,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,好  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:08.33,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:10.06,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,按住那边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:10.93,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:12.55,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:16.34,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,你做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:18.89,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,用了接触型麻醉剂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.89,0:10:21.75,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,该不会是治疗出错了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:25.77,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,喂！ 说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:31.52,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,没有出错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:35.73,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,医生的医术十分高超
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:40.53,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,没有出错？ 为什么你这么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:43.78,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,热衷于教育的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:47.38,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,愿意倾听我女儿歌声的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.38,0:10:50.30,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,还是对我大打出手的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:52.68,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,都是我们所熟知的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:11:00.34,Default,Satoshi,0,0,0,,父亲完全恢复如初了  非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:09.29,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,请问  拍摄要怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:28.49,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,但是… 我没做错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:30.62,Default,Kakei,0,0,0,,不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:35.03,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,你的价值观和我无关
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:40.90,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,一旦接到委托  我就会为了患者的利益全力治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:44.51,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我能做的  仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:57.05,Default,A,0,0,0,,非常抱歉我们的商品给您带来了不便
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:12:01.03,Default,D,0,0,0,,非常抱歉  但本公司不能为其负责
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:02.78,Default,Complainer A,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:05.24,Default,Complainer A,0,0,0,,就算是让程序来向我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:07.66,Default,Complainer A,0,0,0,,也一点诚意都感受不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:10.87,Default,Complainer A,0,0,0,,派人类来！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:16.41,Default,Lady Employee,0,0,0,,最近这种越来越多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:18.39,Default,Lady Employee,0,0,0,,让我来给他们道歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.39,0:12:19.21,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:23.37,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,我来处理  不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:28.72,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,因为精神压力  搞得我胃疼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.09,0:12:31.81,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,这种关联可以切断吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:34.81,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我能做出调整
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:39.48,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,但要是把这些身体的信号全部屏蔽掉的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:41.32,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,哦  我明白你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:44.95,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,这样就会注意不到自己的压力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:48.84,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,在某一天到了极限突然崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:50.77,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,这工作真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:52.88,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,啊  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:53.92,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,归根结底
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:58.09,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,为什么不能用客服 AI 来解决呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.38,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,那种业务
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:03.52,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,AI 的应对当然是无可企及的优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:07.03,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,但是  想要赔礼道歉的人里面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:10.68,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,也有很在意对方是不是「真人」的顾客
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:15.19,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,其中有些人要是知道我是仿生人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:19.48,Default,Complaining Woman,0,0,0,,「你的赔礼道歉与程序向我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:21.35,Default,Complaining Woman,0,0,0,,有什么区别吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:24.57,Default,Complaining Woman,0,0,0,,这种时候应该让人类来道歉才对吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:28.62,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,就会大言不惭地说出这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:33.47,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,虽说我觉得自己也不适合这份工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:43.63,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我换了种咖啡豆  要喝吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:46.17,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:54.12,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:59.65,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,刚才那位… 不会有问题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:03.04,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我希望他没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:10.88,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,以他的情况  光是对症治疗是没法治本的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:18.82,Default,Drunk A,0,0,0,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:22.12,Default,Drunk A,0,0,0,,所以才说你是废物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:23.34,Default,Drunk B,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.01,0:14:25.31,Default,Drunk A,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:27.38,Default,Drunk C,0,0,0,,喂  打起精神来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:28.43,Default,Drunk A,0,0,0,,行啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:41.12,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,我受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.93,0:14:47.05,Default,Lady Employee,0,0,0,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:49.57,Default,Lady Employee,0,0,0,,我马上去您那里一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:52.57,Default,Lady Employee,0,0,0,,好的  好的  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:11.26,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,能胜任这项工作的  就只有无心的机器人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:19.15,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,辞职吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.33,0:15:25.91,Default,President,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:30.82,Default,President,0,0,0,,公司也意识到了你压力的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:32.26,Default,President,0,0,0,,所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:35.73,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,我很高兴您能这么说  但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:37.70,Default,President,0,0,0,,先听我说完嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:43.79,Default,President,0,0,0,,我们把客服的「人类」外包给了专业人士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:48.65,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,在这个时代  自己建房子住的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:51.13,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,都是非常有讲究的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.67,0:15:57.28,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,我自认为我应对顾客时  也是保持了专业素养的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:59.93,Default,President,0,0,0,,不不  我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:04.56,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,不要逼我再说一遍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:08.69,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,你们公司虚拟现实的还原度就是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:12.95,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,我还以为你们能造得一模一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:14.58,Default,President,0,0,0,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:21.19,Default,President,0,0,0,,今后  你和你的部下都不用再应对这些恶意顾客
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:23.85,Default,President,0,0,0,,可以再考虑下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:30.01,Default,Comaplainer B,0,0,0,,都说了  我还要说几次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:34.32,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,叫人类过来确认啊  傻帽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:53.00,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,在应对受冒犯的顾客这方面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:56.53,Default,Apologizer B,0,0,0,,我们有进行特别的针对性训练
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:17:00.96,Default,Apologizer C,0,0,0,,所以说  你真的没必要和他们一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:05.04,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,姑且  这还是第一次转给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:09.14,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,为了防止意外情况  我在外面等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:18.05,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,终于来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:21.54,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,这次给您造成了困扰…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:23.49,Default,Both,0,0,0,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:28.37,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,真是的  你让我等多久了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.41,0:17:33.69,Default,Apologizer C,0,0,0,,我们可以通过工作人员的植入物查看现场的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:38.25,Default,Apologizer C,0,0,0,,他们的应对方式都是按手册行事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:47.12,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,这玩意  怎么看都不对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:48.66,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:53.50,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,这个颜色数值是在误差范围内啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:56.47,Default,Apologizer B,0,0,0,,这样啊  照明的色温呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.25,0:17:59.68,Default,Comapliner B,0,0,0,,你看  完全不一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:02.03,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,这个数值也没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:05.11,Default,Apologizer B,0,0,0,,那再确认一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:06.77,Default,Comapliner B,0,0,0,,无视我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:10.68,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,我也确认一下开尔文值
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:13.70,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:19.20,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,非常抱歉  请再稍候片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.63,0:18:21.88,Default,Apologizer B,0,0,0,,继续
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:22.91,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:27.96,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,真是的  怎么看这都跟我要的壁纸不一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:33.52,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,喂  你们难道认为我是不讲理的魔鬼顾客吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:36.09,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:37.45,Default,Complainer,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:40.26,Default,Complainer,0,0,0,,所以  你们要怎么赔礼道歉啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:44.52,Default,Apologier A,0,0,0,,就结论而言  我们无法道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.33,0:18:54.77,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,喂  你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:56.79,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,这种壁纸给人的观感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:18:59.28,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,会随着照明的色温改变
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:01.28,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,你小子怎么还回嘴啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:05.42,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,喂喂喂  这不是让顾客更激动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:09.68,Default,Apologizer C,0,0,0,,这也是他们的演技
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:12.41,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,虽然像是在回嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:15.67,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,但我这不是找借口  而是在解释
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:20.05,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,谁要你解释了  给我赔礼道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:21.09,Default,Apologizer,0,0,0,,都说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:24.14,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,好吧  那我不要赔礼道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:26.20,Default,Complainer B,0,0,0,,赔礼道歉已经没法收场了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:28.86,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,都说了  照明的色温
Comment: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:33.74,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,分为(灯泡色,3000K)  (温白色,3500K)  (白色,4000K)  (昼白色,5000K)  (昼光色,6000K)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:33.74,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,分为灯泡色  温白色  白色  昼白色  昼光色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:35.40,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,各自用开尔文作为单位…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:37.46,Default,Complainer,0,0,0,,不要跟我扯这些歪理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:38.82,Default,Apologizer B,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:45.20,Default,Apologizer B,0,0,0,,你小子是怎么对待顾客的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.89,0:19:54.96,Default,Apologizer B,0,0,0,,这位顾客…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:05.99,Default,Apologizer B,0,0,0,,您所说的一点都没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:10.23,Default,Apologizer B,0,0,0,,实在是万分抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:19.13,Default,Apologizer C,0,0,0,,让上司用暴力阻止想要讲道理的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:21.35,Default,Apologizer C,0,0,0,,把他作为替罪羊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.37,0:20:24.52,Default,Apologizer C,0,0,0,,这手法对这次这种投诉者是很有效的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:26.62,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,你怎么说得若无其事一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:31.37,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,就算是演技… 这也是灭绝人性的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:33.93,Default,Apologizer C,0,0,0,,你说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:37.88,Default,Apologizer C,0,0,0,,明明他们还闹着要「派人类来」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:40.48,Default,Apologizer C,0,0,0,,真是讽刺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:54.81,Default,Apologizer B,0,0,0,,对方顺利接受了赔礼道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:57.90,Default,Apologizer A,0,0,0,,您觉得怎么样  有让您满意吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:03.15,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,那个… 我这么问可能非常冒犯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:08.01,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,你们是… 人类… 吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:14.24,Default,Apologizer C,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.13,0:21:17.21,Default,Apologizer C,0,0,0,,这是企业机密
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:23.67,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,虽然我没法确定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:27.31,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,但我觉得他们肯定是机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.66,0:21:33.75,Default,Kinosaki,0,0,0,,但即便如此  也没法感觉好受一点
